# 💬 Example Questions You Can Ask

* Which career suits me based on my interests?
* How do I become an AI Engineer?
* What skills should I learn for Data Science?
* Can I switch from Mechanical Engineering to Software Development?
* Which certifications should I pursue?
* How do I prepare for technical interviews?
* What projects should I build for my portfolio?
* What should my career roadmap look like over the next 12 months?

