# 🚀 Why This Project?

Career planning shouldn't rely on generic advice.

This AI Career Bot helps users make smarter decisions by providing:

* Personalized recommendations
* Structured career roadmaps
* Skill-building guidance
* Career transition strategies
* Continuous AI mentorship

It empowers users to confidently navigate their professional journey.

